---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "@/components/ui/Section.astro";
import Button from "@/components/ui/Button.astro";
import { SITE } from "@/shared/config/site";

const title = `Sobre | ${SITE.name}`;
const description =
  "Conheça a história e o processo da Casa Nacoli, gráfica artesanal em Lajeado/RS.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonicalPath="/sobre">
  <Section theme="cream" class="pt-24 pb-12 text-center md:pt-32">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--cn-ink)] md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
      Nossa História
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-black/70">
      A Casa Nacoli nasceu do desejo de trazer alma e personalidade para o papel. Acreditamos que
      cada impresso carrega uma história e merece ser tratado como único.
    </p>
  </Section>

  <Section class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
    <div>
      <div class="aspect-square w-full rounded-2xl bg-black/5 object-cover md:aspect-[4/5]">
        <!-- Placeholder for About Image -->
        <div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center text-black/20">
          Imagem: Processo Artesanal
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--cn-ink)]">
        Artesanal e Independente
      </h2>
      <div class="prose prose-zinc mt-6 text-black/80">
        <p>
          Somos um pequeno estúdio de design e gráfica em Lajeado, Rio Grande do Sul. Fugimos da
          produção em massa para focar nos detalhes que fazem a diferença: a textura do papel, a
          escolha da tipografia, o acabamento manual.
        </p>
        <p>
          Nosso processo combina técnicas tradicionais de impressão com design contemporâneo. Seja
          para identidade visual de pequenas marcas, convites para momentos especiais ou papelaria
          do dia a dia, nosso objetivo é encantar.
        </p>
        <p>
          Valorizamos o tempo, a calma e a qualidade. Cada projeto é desenvolvido com atenção
          individual, garantindo que o resultado final reflita a essência de quem o encomendou.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <Button href="/portfolio">Ver nosso trabalho</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section theme="white" class="text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--cn-ink)] md:text-3xl">
      Nossos Valores
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="px-4">
        <div
          class="mx-auto flex size-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[var(--cn-cream)] text-[var(--cn-terracotta)]"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 256 256"
            ><path
              d="M223.68,66.15l-96-48a8,8,0,0,0-7.36,0l-96,48A8,8,0,0,0,20,73.31V96a84.62,84.62,0,0,0,10.61,41,85.25,85.25,0,0,0,76.54,46,8.12,8.12,0,0,0,1.7,0,8,8,0,0,0,3.69-1.89l8.6-8.6L143,194.34a8,8,0,0,0,11.31,0L240,108.69V73.31A8,8,0,0,0,223.68,66.15ZM121.14,151.72l-13.8,13.8a68.61,68.61,0,0,1-66.23-38A68.08,68.08,0,0,1,36,96V76.69l92-46,84,42v8.2Z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-[var(--cn-ink)]">Qualidade Artesanal</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-black/70">
          Cuidado em cada etapa, do design ao acabamento final.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="px-4">
        <div
          class="mx-auto flex size-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[var(--cn-cream)] text-[var(--cn-terracotta)]"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 256 256"
            ><path
              d="M128,24A104,104,0,1,0,232,128,104.11,104.11,0,0,0,128,24Zm0,192a88,88,0,1,1,88-88A88.1,88.1,0,0,1,128,216Zm-16-80a16,16,0,1,1,16,16A16,16,0,0,1,112,136Zm32-32V72a8,8,0,0,0-16,0v32a8,8,0,0,0,16,0Z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-[var(--cn-ink)]">Atendimento Próximo</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-black/70">
          Conversa direta e transparente para entender sua necessidade.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="px-4">
        <div
          class="mx-auto flex size-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[var(--cn-cream)] text-[var(--cn-terracotta)]"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 256 256"
            ><path
              d="M224,176a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H192v24a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V184H152a8,8,0,0,1,0-16h24V144a8,8,0,0,1,16,0v24h24A8,8,0,0,1,224,176ZM116.35,53.28a8,8,0,0,0-11,2.07L92.79,72.43,87.32,94.29a8,8,0,0,0,5.39,9.39l22.21,6.34,19.34-11,26.54-9.65a8,8,0,0,0,3.64-11.83ZM204.62,40.19a39.84,39.84,0,0,0-56.44,0l-58,58-5.34-5.34a8,8,0,0,0-11.31,11.31l5.34,5.34L35.21,153.24A40,40,0,0,0,28,197.35L42.66,234a8,8,0,0,0,7.09,5.16,7.84,7.84,0,0,0,3.31-.73L90,223.79a40,40,0,0,0,44.11-7.21l43.72-43.71,5.34,5.34a8,8,0,0,0,11.31-11.31l-5.34-5.34,58-58a39.85,39.85,0,0,0,0-56.44l-26.49-26.49A39.9,39.9,0,0,0,204.62,40.19ZM78.69,212.48,51.84,223.22,62.58,196.37a24,24,0,0,1,4.32-26.49l38.29-38.29,22.18,22.18-38.29,38.29A23.93,23.93,0,0,1,78.69,212.48Zm110.15-95.27L145.13,73.49l26.49-26.49a24,24,0,0,1,33.81,0l26.49,26.49a24,24,0,0,1,0,33.81Z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-[var(--cn-ink)]">Design com Propósito</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-black/70">
          Estética que funciona e comunica a essência da sua marca.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
